pen_count</code> is <code>3</code> (greater than <code>0</code>), so decrem=
ent it to <code>2</code>.</p></li><li><p><b>')'</b>: <code>unmatched_open_c=
ount</code> is <code>2</code> (greater than <code>0</code>), so decrement i=
