rom the beginning of the array and the other (<code>stack2</code>) grow fro=
m the end. They grow towards each other.</p><p></p><h3>Logic and Algorithm<=
/h3><p></p><ol start=3D"1"><li><p><b>Data Structure:</b> Define a <code>two=
Stacks</code> structure. It should contain a pointer to the shared array, t=
